yeezus.pcb

Class PCB

  • java.lang.Object
    • yeezus.pcb.PCB

  • public class PCB
extends java.lang.Object
    A class to hold various information relating to the processes run by the Yeezus Operating System. The data held by these instances are to be used by the Driver and related classes for their interactions with the processes stored in Memory.
    Version:
    2.0
    Author:
    Mark Zeagler, Jessica Brummel

    • Nested Class Summary

      Nested Classes 
      Modifier and Type Class and Description
      static class  PCB.Status
      An enumeration of the different statuses that this process will set as.
